data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT!! Why pay more for a new build? This near new move-in-ready home finished in 2023 gives you all the benefits of a new home including an a/c unit, furnace, tankless water heater, kitchen appliances, roof, electrical, landscaping, fence and blinds. Also, this home has a full unfinished basement for added living space and equity. Welcome Home! This 2023 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom, 2-car attached garage Meritage energy-efficient two-story home is in the new and desirable Prairie Center Villages community. This immaculate home with stunning exterior has upgrades throughout. As you enter the home you are greeted by a spacious flex room which could be a great formal dining room or bright office. Down the hall, the beautiful kitchen is the focal point of the main floor space showcasing white cabinetry, white quartz countertops, a large island, full walk-in pantry, stainless steel appliances, EVP flooring and warm grey carpet. Enjoy the adjoining eat-in dining space. The ample family room brings in lots of natural light. The nearby 1/2 bath is an added touch.  Off the living room is the finished oversized two car garage. Step outside to the large backyard which is nicely landscaped for your enjoyment and outdoor relaxation. The upper-level features 4 wonderful bedrooms. The large primary suite offers a spacious 4pc bathroom and walk-in closet. Down the hallway are 3 bedrooms, plus a full bathroom. The laundry room is conveniently located upstairs. Another highlight is the full unfinished basement which is perfect for future expansion. This space could be finished to provide an additional bedroom, office or rec room. The nearby Prairie Center Shopping Center is home to grocery, dining, trails, and parks all within 5 minutes from home. Location, location! Move in today and experience the best Brighton’s Prairie Center Villages has to offer.
